## How to Install

From a CDN:

```html
<head>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/heartml@0.13.0"></script>
</head>
```

From a package:

```shell
npm i heartml
```

```js
import { HeartElement } from "heartml"
```

